{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/loop1.gif?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is a puzzle game that seamlessly blends 2D card mechanics with 3D scene transitions, offering a unique perspective-shifting gameplay experience. In this game, you will gather clues from immersive 3D environments and apply them to solve puzzles on a 2D card table. Meanwhile, your actions on the card table can also influence changes in the 3D world. Uncover related clues and piece together the unfolding story.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/jietu3.png?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oh, your senses have been separated. Now, use these unique senses to solve the puzzles:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hand</strong>: Touch and pick up objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Eye</strong>: Observe objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Think</strong>: Analyze and examine objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/loop2.gif?t=1739758481\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">These separated senses will become crucial elements in your puzzle-solving journey. Use them wisely!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, different cards have &quot;fusion relationships.&quot; Combine them to explore more possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/Snipaste_2025-02-11_01-44-39.jpg?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soon, you will witness something even more incredible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can break free from the 2D perspective and step into the 3D scene! This game seamlessly shifts between 2D and 3D perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The objects in the 3D environment are interconnected with the cards on the 2D table.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use 3D objects to alter the cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to change objects in the 3D world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/jietu7_1920_.png?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the story progresses, you will uncover more about this enigmatic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;It&quot; made everything disappear, yet the rain that night never ceased. Thus, I embarked on a journey to find the answers. Why did I become myself?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Switching between different ways of thinking is also a key strategy!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different thoughts may lead to different outcomes.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3510730?t=1739758481","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3510730?t=1739758481","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/45e969ff6222033abd262fc035e570831b8d2261/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739758481","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/45e969ff6222033abd262fc035e570831b8d2261/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739758481","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/loop1.gif?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is a puzzle game that seamlessly blends 2D card mechanics with 3D scene transitions, offering a unique perspective-shifting gameplay experience. In this game, you will gather clues from immersive 3D environments and apply them to solve puzzles on a 2D card table. Meanwhile, your actions on the card table can also influence changes in the 3D world. Uncover related clues and piece together the unfolding story.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/jietu3.png?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oh, your senses have been separated. Now, use these unique senses to solve the puzzles:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hand</strong>: Touch and pick up objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Eye</strong>: Observe objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Think</strong>: Analyze and examine objects.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/loop2.gif?t=1739758481\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">These separated senses will become crucial elements in your puzzle-solving journey. Use them wisely!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, different cards have &quot;fusion relationships.&quot; Combine them to explore more possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/Snipaste_2025-02-11_01-44-39.jpg?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soon, you will witness something even more incredible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can break free from the 2D perspective and step into the 3D scene! This game seamlessly shifts between 2D and 3D perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The objects in the 3D environment are interconnected with the cards on the 2D table.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use 3D objects to alter the cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to change objects in the 3D world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/extras/jietu7_1920_.png?t=1739758481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the story progresses, you will uncover more about this enigmatic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;It&quot; made everything disappear, yet the rain that night never ceased. Thus, I embarked on a journey to find the answers. Why did I become myself?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Switching between different ways of thinking is also a key strategy!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different thoughts may lead to different outcomes.</p>","developers":["UnstableSalt"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510730/header.jpg?t=1739758481","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257094641,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094641/movie480.mp4?t=1739239770","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094641/movie_max.mp4?t=1739239770"},"name":"Loop\u73af\u5f62\u8c2c\u8bba\u5148\u5bfcPV","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257094641/ede1ec1d4cdf5f65d4097b0958047b059b2f3da4/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739239770","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257094641/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739239770","max":"http://video.akamai.s